name: Extreme Boss Maker 1000
text: I DO NOT RECOMMEND CALLING THIS PLACE! Please, DON'T! I called this place because I just heard of it, it actually sounded cool honestly hearing that they answer ANY questions you may have. But that was not the case. I called the place waiting for someone to pick up and then after a couple of seconds this one lady (who is actaully very rude) answered. She wanted to know my question and I told her the question that I had. Then she hung up. Afterwards it became a call hangup battle, it was very weird. after that she answered. I told her "why are you hanging up on me" and she said "you probally aren't asking an appropriate question" And I told her "But I heard this place answers any questions" and she said that they don't do that and hung up on me again. And then I tried to call again and it took awhile but then she picked up again I told her that "If you don't answer questions how come Matt Lauer the host of The Today Show ask a question live on air and asked "What is Barbie's full name?" why is that?" and then she hung up AGAIN! It doesn't make sense! This place is a shame this place does NOT answer questions and it's a lie. Like I said I dont recommend calling, all it is is rudeness and lies. It's not worth it. Foy Information Desk, this is the best review for you!
